{"tid":2182187,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"採樣點「做票站安全過做檢測」","createTime":"2020-08-31T07:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T07:03:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f361bc7b3a3d14ac404250ff46b8a9c32b1608c","tid":2182187,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SYR4VWNWL5GSPJJHS4RO5JBM4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSYR4VWNWL5GSPJJHS4RO5JBM4Q%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=aa93bdf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSYR4VWNWL5GSPJJHS4RO5JBM4Q%2F&h=68c8098b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SYR4VWNWL5GSPJJHS4RO5JBM4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n採樣點「做票站安全過做檢測」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全港141個檢測中心中逾半曾是去年區議會選舉或2016年立法會選舉票站。本報昨日前往部份曾為票站的檢測中心觀察，發現皆為大型社區會堂或體育館主場館，相對寬敞；有當區居民批評政府只當疫情為政治工具，刻意阻撓選舉，「做票站仲安全過做檢測中心㖭，因為唔使除口罩」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ui2C-CVyDrUYAwcKrtjv21EJwEI=/1173x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EMMRK6L2YJATRD4I4N6XXVNQLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fui2C-CVyDrUYAwcKrtjv21EJwEI%3D%2F1173x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEMMRK6L2YJATRD4I4N6XXVNQLY.jpg&h=9d4c0794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■摩士公園體育館檢測中心內放有口罩、搓手液等醫療物資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民促疫情穩定後恢復選舉<br />\n<br />\n疫情重災區黃大仙區的九個檢測中心中，有五個曾是票站，其中摩士公園體育館有多名職員看守，偌大的場館尚未安放隔板、椅子等設備，只擺放部份口罩、搓手液等醫療物資；竹園體育館及鳳德社區中心更重門深鎖。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙選民柯先生表示，政府選址主要是大型場地，例如竹園體育館，認為無論用作票站或檢測中心感染風險都很低，「做票站仲安全過做檢測中心㖭，因為唔使除口罩」。他。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一居民梁先生指出，選舉是集體行為，「有人就做得，邊度都應該做得。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e89c9218992f4f2d2636434509573b998431fe6c","tid":2182187,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"檢測站係武漢病毒高危地區"}]}